# Support

## Where to ask
- GitHub Issues: https://github.com/Arjun2729/ANNPACK/issues

## What to include
- Your OS + Python version
- `annpack --version`
- The exact command you ran
- Any error output (copy/paste)
- Whether `ANNPACK_OFFLINE=1` was set

## Security issues
Please follow the instructions in `SECURITY.md` instead of filing a public issue.
